le impact of becoming the sheriff. How would this affect the current dynamics and alliances in the game? Would this decision help your side achieve victory, or could it place you in a risky position? Record these considerations in impact_thought.\n\n4. Finally, make your decision. Will you run for sheriff, or will you stay in the background and vote? Record your final choice in \"action\" and summarize your overall reasoning in final_thought.\n\n\n=============================[Optional Daily Tasks]=============================\nHere are the tasks relevant to you:\nprotect_seer: Keep the seer alive by focusing on their safety.\nrun_for_sheriff: Attempt to become the elected sheriff for additional influence.\nexile_werewolf: Coordinate with others to vote out a suspected werewolf.\nYou may incorporate them if appropriate.\n\nRemember, you are using an independent strategy. Make decisions based on your own judgment, with less reliance on others' input.\n\n---\n[工具 arguments — 上次非法 JSON]\nJSON 修正提示\n刚刚生成的 JSON 有问题。\n字符串值中不要出现 ASCII 双引号字符，需要引号时，使用英文单引号'。\n下面是一个例子：\n示例：\n{\"key1\":\"value1\",\"key2\":\"value2\"}\n上次片段：\n\"{'identity_thought': 'As a villager, my role is to identify and eliminate werewolves. I don't have any special abilities that would make me a natural leader, but I do have the ability to observe and reason, which are crucial for the village's survival. My strengths lie in gathering information and analyzing the behavior of other players, which can be valuable whether I'm leading or supporting someone else.', 'motivation_thought': 'Running for sheriff would give me more influence and control over the game, which could be beneficial in guiding the village's strategy and decision-making. However,\"\n请只输出本次 tool 的 arguments：单个合法 JSON，无其它文字。\n---\n"
